{"tid":1640468,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【天琦上訴】數百人庭外聲援上訴　有學生稱梁天琦為這代年輕人啟蒙","createTime":"2019-10-09T03:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T03:38:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"05b084d8972d2fe08180a4f09cb64e191271dbe2","tid":1640468,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1485115_1_L_20191009111613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1485115_1_L_20191009111613.jpg&h=0d189c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485115-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485115-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ05YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=7fa4c145\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485115-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cd41d642\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485115-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n高等法院審理旺角騷亂中三名被告梁天琦、盧建民、黃家駒的上訴案件，數百名身穿黑衣的人士及學生等到庭外聲援。<br />\n<br />\n有到場聲援的教育大學歷史學系二年級學生表示，希望令梁天琦知道仍有一班香港人支持他，他形容梁天琦是這代年輕人的啟蒙，他又對香港司法制度有信心，若果上訴失敗，他依然會繼續支持梁天琦。<br />\n<br />\n有理工大學設計學系二年級學生認為，梁天琦參選補選令香港的政治光譜更多元化，本土派的政見可以完全代表自己，令她重新找到自己的政治取態。"}]}